<FIRST>r a PM-OzoneStudy     11-16 0593</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Ozone Study,0609</SECOND>
<HEAD>Unexplained Ozone Losses Found Near Antarctica</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: RETRANSMITTING a0506 to fix slugline.</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By MALCOLM RITTER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>AP Science Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
